{"tid":1692000,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"原來簡迪當年係比人迫簽約去李城","createTime":"2019-11-04T01:32:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T07:24:43.000Z","uid":77355,"like":279,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"40bdf602e4f7bfb23888ab71a78e9e61bd3a9c7f","tid":1692000,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T01:32:07.000Z","msg":"藍狐於14-15球季重返英超，維猜放水沒想像中多，華殊簽下了另一前紅魔森遜、傷癒不久的史篤城中堅侯夫等，這些都是2016年英超冠軍的骨幹成員。人生可控制的東西實在太少，2015年球隊在泰國爆出性醜聞，領隊皮雅臣下台，華殊留低輔助走馬上任的雲尼亞里。然後，冠軍最後一塊拼圖，簡迪來了。原來當年簡迪加盟也有段鮮為人知的插曲。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">話說華殊在卡昂發現「一個打兩個」的鐵人簡迪後，決心不簽不走，甚至冒險走法津罅，與法國線人夾住簡迪上飛機返英國，又「訛稱」馬賽無意簽下他，而當時簡迪根本還未來得切通知其經理人。由此可見，球員無名氣的話，有時會遇到不少「慘事」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在英國，簡迪被沒收手機，獨個兒被推上轉會談判桌，最終半推半就下簽約，簽約完成後才可以通知經理人過來接他</span></span>，之後的故事都成為歷史。李城一路爆冷，奪得1賠5000的英超冠軍，整支冠軍隊有10人來自華殊的操作，總共只花2000多萬鎊，性價比堪稱歷史之最。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：毒毒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：華殊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：嗱依家馬賽一定唔會簽你嫁啦，不如跟我返英超啦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我。。。想。。。等多陣可唔可以？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：等你老母呀同我上機！<br />\n(毒毒比人夾左上機去李城)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:吓。。你話既藍軍竟然係李城！？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：屌我都冇呃你。李城咪一樣藍色！快撚手簽約呢！ 喂，交手機呀！<br />\n(之後部手機比人沒收左)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：屌你老母快撚啲簽啦，睇咩呀！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：吓得果 兩萬幾鎊週薪。。。。。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：屌你老母吖，你唔撚簽冇得走！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我簽囉。。。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：簽好咗叫你經理人接你。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：依條毒撚真係好恰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔怪之得毒毒咁想離開李城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a36124330145a5319bbc5d70d5651a69a5dd4a49","tid":1692000,"uid":47268,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T01:34:48.000Z","msg":"笑4"},{"pid":"cee6cff29ca0c1a475c6c5785c60bd1f7819b0fc","tid":1692000,"uid":22488,"like":115,"dislike":0,"score":115,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T01:36:32.000Z","msg":"但踢到有英超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8580181ec99adbd3ccfad0c8a60a61ea311831","tid":1692000,"uid":11895,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T01:37:23.000Z","msg":"佢個陣有兩萬幾週薪算係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cccbf79c0d665fbf2973710837f8d06e4cae52d3","tid":1692000,"uid":77355,"like":172,"dislike":0,"score":172,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T01:40:39.000Z","msg":"李斯特城前鋒占美華迪接受法國傳媒訪問，被問到對前隊友尼高路簡迪有何感想，華迪表示很喜歡和他有隊友，因為他非常可愛，曾表示想不駕車、於家中跑到訓練場<br />\n痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a323a497309d22ed56ba152349834289a87933a1","tid":1692000,"uid":48222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cccbf79c0d665fbf2973710837f8d06e4cae52d3","tid":1692000,"uid":77355,"like":172,"dislike":0,"score":172,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T01:40:39.000Z","msg":"李斯特城前鋒占美華迪接受法國傳媒訪問，被問到對前隊友尼高路簡迪有何感想，華迪表示很喜歡和他有隊友，因為他非常可愛，曾表示想不駕車、於家中跑到訓練場<br />\n痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm